title: Congratulations to MAgIC Lab undergraduate student Kaitian Chao on his Best Thesis Award
description: Kaitian Chao's undergraduate thesis paper: An Adversarial Meta Learning-based Dynamic Modeling For Robotic Fish, supervised by Prof. Yang Wang, won the Best Thesis Award among all the 2024 SIST undergraduate theses. Kaitian and Professor Wang were awarded by the Dean Jingyi Yu.
